-- =============================================================================
-- Calendar events (all belong to u1)
-- Spread across past, present, and future relative to CURRENT_DATE so the
-- calendar always has content regardless of when the seed is applied.
-- Event types: ‘date’, ‘hangout’, ‘call’, ‘text’, ‘other’
-- All events start as status=’planned’ with no outcome reported.
-- Note: events in the past (negative intervals) will show as needing a report
-- in the UI until the user logs in and marks them as happened/fell_through.
-- =============================================================================
